  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aimed to characterize swallowing disorders in minimally consciousness patients
      after brain traumatic injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      After inclusion, the patients will underwent a videofluoroscopy and the Wessex Head Injury
      Matrix.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
